          </constraints>
          <rules>
            <rule id="d7f9-2d1a-8b15-ed4a" name="Liber Heresius" hidden="false">
              <description>In a mission where there is a choice of table edge, the Inquisitor must take a Leadership test before the game and if this is passed he may choose the deployment zone for his army rather than rolling a dice for it. If he fails the test on a double 6, then the enemy player may choose his deployment zone without rolling for it.</description>
            </rule>
