          </constraints>
          <rules>
            <rule id="aaf6-6311-3c29-03d4" name="Psychic Hood" hidden="false">
              <description>Declare you&apos;ll use the Psychic Hood after an opponent ahs successfully made a Psychic test, but before they have resolved the power. Each player rolls a D6 and adds their respective model&apos;s Leadership value. If the Space Marine beats the opposing model&apos;s score then the psychic power is nullified and may not be used that turn. Otherwise the power is unaffected. The Hood may be used each time an enemy model uses a power.</description>
            </rule>
          </rules>
